### Generate Image with SDXL (Stable Diffusion XL)
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/images
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "A steampunk airship floating in cloudy skies",
  "model": "sdxl",
  "width": 1024,
